%% ODH Dashboard - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAuth as Kubernetes API Server<br/>(SubjectAccessReview)
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (loopback)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant MRUI as model-registry-ui<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant GAUI as gen-ai-ui<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Note over Browser,Gateway: Flow 1: User Accesses Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS (serving cert)<br/>User token forwarded
    KRBP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Can user list project.openshift.io/projects?
    K8sAuth-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080 loopback)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups
    Backend-->>KRBP: Static SPA assets (index.html)
    KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTML/JS/CSS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: API Proxy (e.g., Notebook CRUD)

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/notebooks (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAuth-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Forwarded-Access-Token
    Backend->>Backend: requestSecurityGuard<br/>(namespace + ownership check)
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR (HTTPS/443)<br/>User's Bearer token (passthrough)
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Notebook Created
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser,MRUI: Flow 3: Module Federation Plugin Loading

    Browser->>KRBP: GET /_mf/modelRegistry/remoteEntry.js<br/>(HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>MRUI: Proxy (HTTPS/8043)<br/>Bearer token authorization
    MRUI-->>Backend: remoteEntry.js
    Backend-->>Browser: Module Federation chunk

    Browser->>KRBP: GET /model-registry/api/models<br/>(HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>MRUI: Proxy /api/models (HTTPS/8043)<br/>Bearer token
    MRUI-->>Backend: Model data
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser,Thanos: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Query

    Browser->>KRBP: GET /api/prometheus?query=...<br/>(HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Forwarded-Access-Token
    Backend->>Thanos: PromQL query (HTTPS/9092)<br/>User Bearer token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics data
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON metrics response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 5: WebSocket Resource Watch

    Browser->>KRBP: WS /wss/k8s/... (WSS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: WS upgrade (WS/8080)
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch request (HTTPS/443)<br/>User token passthrough
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Stream: resource events
    Backend-->>Browser: Stream: WS frames
